error.message: Parameter $alias_repository of method Drupal\pathauto\AliasStorageHelper::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Path\AliasRepositoryInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\path_alias\AliasRepositoryInterface.

Parameter $alias_manager of method Drupal\pathauto\AliasUniquifier::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Path\AliasManagerInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\path_alias\AliasManagerInterface.

Parameter $alias_storage of method Drupal\pathauto\LegacyAliasStorageHelper::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Path\AliasStorageInterface: \Drupal\Core\Path\AliasStorage is deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use the "path_alias.repository" service instead, or the entity storage handler for the "path_alias" entity type for CRUD methods.

Parameter $entity_manager of method Drupal\pathauto\Plugin\migrate\source\PathautoPattern::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityManagerInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0.
Call to deprecated function entity_get_display(). Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use EntityDisplayRepositoryInterface::getViewDisplay() instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to pathauto.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
